@startuml

' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
'  教师组卷发布考试时序图 (精简版)
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────

!theme plain
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "monospace"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam ArrowColor #000000
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #000000
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActorBorderColor #000000
skinparam SequenceBoxBorderColor #000000
skinparam SequenceBoxBackgroundColor #FFFFFF

title <b>教师组卷发布考试时序图</b>

actor 教师 as Teacher
participant "前端\n(Vue3 + Element Plus)" as Frontend
participant "PaperService\n(试卷服务)" as PaperService
participant "ExamService\n(考试服务)" as ExamService
participant "QuestionService\n(题目服务)" as QuestionService
database "MySQL\n(数据库)" as MySQL

== 1. 添加试题 ==
Teacher -> Frontend : 填写题目信息
Frontend -> QuestionService : POST /api/questions
QuestionService -> MySQL : INSERT INTO questions
MySQL --> QuestionService : 保存成功
QuestionService --> Frontend : 200 OK
Frontend --> Teacher : 题目添加成功

== 2. 创建试卷 ==
Teacher -> Frontend : 配置组卷规则，选择题目
Frontend -> PaperService : POST /api/papers
PaperService -> MySQL : INSERT INTO papers
MySQL --> PaperService : 保存成功
PaperService --> Frontend : 200 OK

== 3. 发布考试 ==
Teacher -> Frontend : 设置考试时间，关联试卷
Frontend -> ExamService : POST /api/exams
ExamService -> MySQL : INSERT INTO exams (status=DRAFT)
MySQL --> ExamService : 保存成功
ExamService --> Frontend : 200 OK
Frontend -> ExamService : POST /api/exams/{id}/publish
ExamService -> MySQL : UPDATE status='PUBLISHED'
MySQL --> ExamService : 发布成功
ExamService --> Frontend : 200 OK
Frontend --> Teacher : 考试发布成功

@enduml
